Class PictureMarkerSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.symbol.Symbol

          • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.symbol.PictureMarkerSymbol

  • public class PictureMarkerSymbol
extends MarkerSymbol
    Marker symbols are used to draw points and multipoints on the graphics layer. PictureMarkerSymbol uses an image as a marker.
    Author:
    Justin Merz
